285
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:28,349
Oh, I wasn't the one who made a promise

286
00:18:28,629 --> 00:18:30,070
at the board meeting.

287
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:31,540
You didn't object to it then either.

288
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:31,990
You…

289
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:33,869
Do you know why

290
00:18:34,030 --> 00:18:36,909
