you are on top of me?

291
00:18:37,149 --> 00:18:37,589
I…

292
00:18:42,070 --> 00:18:43,909
During the time when
you lost your memory,

293
00:18:44,149 --> 00:18:45,909
you had split into another personality.

294
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:55,790
Only after contacting me

295
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:57,070
will you return to normal.

296
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:00,550
Do you mean

297
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:03,149
that I transform every time I sleep

298
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:05,310
and only you can change me back?

299
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:10,349
This other personality can wreak havoc.

300
00:19:10,909 --> 00:19:11,829
Only I can suppress

301
00:19:11,829 --> 00:19:13,270
this personality inside you.

302
00:19:14,629 --> 00:19:15,950
Having you live here

303
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:18,189
is purely to prevent you
from transforming.

304
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:20,510
In that way, you will have more time

305
00:19:20,510 --> 00:19:22,030
to fix the game.

306
00:19:26,629 --> 00:19:28,389
Okay, I'll stay.

307
00:19:34,909 --> 00:19:35,710
Get to work, then.

308
00:19:37,470 --> 00:19:39,189
You are inhumane, do you know that?

309
00:19:39,909 --> 00:19:40,510
Now?

310
00:19:40,869 --> 00:19:42,310
Everyone is off work now.

311
00:19:42,310 --> 00:19:43,829
You have 14 days left.

312
00:19:47,429 --> 00:19:48,030
Okay.

313
00:19:50,270 --> 00:19:50,990
Hard drive.

314
00:20:26,450 --> 00:20:27,389
You should get off work.

315
00:20:27,750 --> 00:20:29,470
Mr. Xiao, you don't need
to worry about me.

316
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:30,230
Let me be.

317
00:20:30,389 --> 00:20:31,030
I'm not sleepy.

318
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:32,750
I want to finish this bit of data.

319
00:20:33,850 --> 00:20:35,550
Even if you don't want to sleep,
I want to.

320
00:20:36,470 --> 00:20:37,510
You can go ahead and sleep.

321
00:20:37,510 --> 00:20:38,510
I don't mind.

322
00:20:38,669 --> 00:20:40,030
What does it have to do with me?

323
00:20:42,230 --> 00:20:43,710
You will transform when you sleep.

324
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:45,230
Then, you'll torment me again.

325
00:20:46,189 --> 00:20:47,230
Save your file now.

326
00:20:47,669 --> 00:20:48,230
Shut it down.

327
00:20:50,550 --> 00:20:51,270
Oh, that's right.

328
00:20:51,629 --> 00:20:53,310
I almost forgot that this is a thing.

329
00:21:08,389 --> 00:21:09,310
Well…

330
00:21:10,230 --> 00:21:13,270
Mr. Xiao, there's just one bed.

331
00:21:14,410 --> 00:21:15,230
What did you expect?

332
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:18,270
I can sleep in the living room

333
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:21,389
or on the couch.

334
00:21:24,149 --> 00:21:25,389
You can sleep on the couch,

335
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:27,330
but do you want me to sleep
on the couch too?

336
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:30,629
Get into bed.

337
00:21:51,589 --> 00:21:53,310
I'm just doing this for work.

338
00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:17,470
Mr. Xiao,

339
00:22:19,389 --> 00:22:21,109
the air conditioner is not working.

340
00:22:21,510 --> 00:22:22,829
Don't you feel hot?

341
00:22:24,629 --> 00:22:25,550
It's 23 degrees.

342
00:22:27,410 --> 00:22:28,389
Do you want some water?

343
00:22:31,230 --> 00:22:31,829
No.

344
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:35,550
Why don't you go to the toilet?

345
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,730
Are we just going to sleep like this?

346
00:22:49,829 --> 00:22:50,589
What else?

347
00:22:53,990 --> 00:22:54,829
Give me your hand.

348
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:57,310
What for?

349
00:22:57,750 --> 00:22:59,149
If we aren't physically in contact,

350
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:01,310
