Hey, I'm sorry.

354
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:56,030
Hold them up for me for a bit.

355
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:57,389
I'll be there in about half an hour.

356
00:23:57,389 --> 00:23:58,790
You always have a good memory,

357
