377
00:24:50,230 --> 00:24:51,909
That evil Xiao the Merciless.

378
00:24:52,510 --> 00:24:53,990
Do you treat me as a data entry girl?

379
00:24:55,730 --> 00:24:57,349
It's really miserable to be an employee.

380
00:24:59,909 --> 00:25:02,310
I must make you into a
non-playable character

381
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:06,389
that labors in the game.

382
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:36,189
Hey, I'm here.

383
00:25:36,189 --> 00:25:36,950
Where are you?

384
00:25:37,109 --> 00:25:38,149
Keep walking inside.

385
00:25:38,149 --> 00:25:38,950
I'll come to get you.

386
00:25:39,109 --> 00:25:39,589
Okay.

387
00:25:47,990 --> 00:25:49,109
You're finally here.

388
00:25:49,470 --> 00:25:51,790
Miss Chen came here especially
from Australia

389
00:25:51,909 --> 00:25:53,349
just to invest in our game.

390
00:25:53,669 --> 00:25:55,030
You must remember

391
00:25:55,030 --> 00:25:56,149
to have the best attitude.

392
00:25:56,349 --> 00:25:58,550
Don't leave her hanging halfway
like the last time.

393
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:00,629
I'll try my best.

394
00:26:02,230 --> 00:26:04,109
This deal is very important to us.

395
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:05,829
If you guys have a pleasant chat

396
00:26:06,040 --> 00:26:07,760
