a shareholder.

397
00:26:09,109 --> 00:26:10,230
Got it, bro.

398
00:26:10,230 --> 00:26:11,189
I know it.

399
00:26:19,990 --> 00:26:21,070
Let me introduce you

400
00:26:21,310 --> 00:26:22,270
to Miss Chen,

401
00:26:22,389 --> 00:26:24,429
the famous overseas real estate tycoon.

402
00:26:24,990 --> 00:26:26,230
This is my brother, Xiao Ran,

403
00:26:26,230 --> 00:26:27,330
President of Shanhai Group.

404
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,389
Hello.

405
00:26:29,589 --> 00:26:31,990
Mr. Xiao is indeed a young talent.

406
00:26:32,429 --> 00:26:33,909
Handsome and talented.

407
00:26:34,389 --> 00:26:35,349
As expected,

408
00:26:35,429 --> 00:26:36,629
