409
00:26:38,230 --> 00:26:39,230
What is this?

410
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:40,429
A small gift.

411
00:26:41,909 --> 00:26:44,149
Oh, surprisingly thoughtful.

412
00:26:45,230 --> 00:26:46,230
