440
00:27:51,990 --> 00:27:53,909
So be it. It doesn't matter.

441
00:27:53,909 --> 00:27:55,470
I'm sending you the address now.

442
00:27:55,710 --> 00:27:57,710
I'm here to help you.

443
00:27:58,829 --> 00:28:01,589
Miss Chen is not only a high achiever
in the real estate industry,

444
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:03,470
